      "rationale": "Three-level mesh refinement study (4.2 M, 8.7 M, 17.1 M cells) performed at the 5 L/min 3000 RPM operating point. GCI for relative hemolysis index = 3.8%, satisfying the < 5% threshold. Gradation 2 requirement met."
