      "rationale": "FDA generic centrifugal pump geometry is identical to the simulation domain. Validation uses ovine blood at physiological hematocrit (35–40%) across the same 5 flow-speed combinations defined in the COU. Validation scenario relevance is high; Gradation 2 satisfied."
